text: Speaker of the House of Commons can refer to: *Speaker of the House of Commons (United Kingdom), which has historically comprised: **Speaker of the House of Commons of England (-1706) **Speaker of the House of Commons of Great Britain (1707-1800) **Speaker of the House of Commons of the United Kingdom (1801-) *Speaker of the Canadian House of Commons (1867-) *Speaker of the Northern Ireland House of Commons
title: Speaker of the House of Commons
